OL,3,CScotland announces World Cup squad
OL,4,Cwith Stewart and Curtis in team
OL,6,FSouthampton striker Ross Stewart and
OL,7,Fteenage Rangers winger Findlay Curtis
OL,8,Fhave been named in Scotland's squad
OL,9,Ffor the 2026 World Cup.
OL,11,FStewart, 29, has not been in the
OL,12,Fnational squad since 2022, his first
OL,13,Finternational appearance, due to
OL,14,Finjury, while Curtis, 19, made his
OL,15,Fdebut during a friendly against Japan
OL,16,Fin March earlier this year.
OL,18,FChe Adams, Lyndon Dykes, Lawrence
OL,19,FShankland and George Hirst will join
OL,20,FStewart as Scotland's striking options
OL,21,Fin the 26-man team.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
