OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779282676
OL,3,CScotland announces World Cup squad
OL,4,Cwith Stewart and Curtis in team
OL,6,FHearts' Craig Gordon is one of three
OL,7,Fgoalkeepers to make the team, along
OL,8,Fwith Angus Gunn and Liam Kelly.
OL,10,FBen Gannon-Doak has also been
OL,11,Fincluded, after making three
OL,12,Fappearances off the bench for
OL,13,FBournemouth since suffering a serious
OL,14,Fhamstring injury in Scotland's win
OL,15,Fover Denmark in November.
OL,17,FHe joins Ryan Christie, Curtis, Lewis
OL,18,FFerguson, Billy Gilmour, John McGinn,
OL,19,FKenny McLean and Scott McTominay as
OL,20,Fchoices for midfield.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
