PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779282676
OL,3,CScotland announces World Cup squad
OL,4,Cwith Stewart and Curtis in team
OL,6,FThe defenders are Grant Hanley, Jack
OL,7,FHendry, Aaron Hickey, Dom Hyam, Scott
OL,8,FMcKenna, Nathan Patterson, Anthony
OL,9,FRalston, Andy Robertson, John Souttar
OL,10,Fand Kieran Tierney.
OL,12,FThe Scottish team are in Group C for
OL,13,Fthe contest, which will officially
OL,14,Fkick off in the US and Mexico on June
OL,15,F12.
OL,17,FThe squad will train at Inter Miami's
OL,18,FFlorida Blue Training Center, ahead of
OL,19,Ftheir games against Haiti on June 14,
OL,20,FMorocco on June 19 and Brazil on June
OL,21,F24.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
